Which team won the 2020 World Series?.sql:
SELECT team_name
FROM teams
WHERE yearID = 2020 AND WSWin = 'Y';

Which team won the World Series in 2019?.sql:
SELECT team_name
FROM teams
WHERE yearID = 2019 AND WSWin = 'Y';

Which player holds the record for the mo.sql:
SELECT p.nameFirst, p.nameLast, MAX(b.b_HR) AS most_home_runs
FROM batting b
JOIN people p ON b.playerID = p.playerID;

Which team won the first ever World Seri.sql:
SELECT team_name
FROM teams
WHERE yearID = (SELECT MIN(yearID) FROM teams WHERE WSWin = 'Y');
